inite order in the sense that the free energy is smaller than any power of\n$h-h_c(\\beta)$ in the neighborhood of the critical point and that disorder does\nnot modify at all the nature of the transition. We also provide results on the\nbehavior of the paths of the random field in the limit $N \\to \\infty$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2016 18:45:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-06"}
