ight is dark, otherwise known as Olbers' paradox.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2016 20:06:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2016 21:09:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-19"}
