 theories and possible directions for future\ndevelopment will also be discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2016 05:22:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2016 16:58:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2017 03:59:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-06"}
